N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 176.17 - Open to public

State Regulations

All courses approved pursuant to this Part shall be open to
all members of the public regardless of the membership of the prospective
student in any real estate board, or real estate related professional society
or organization. Notes
